<div id="outline-container-org8fb49fb" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org8fb49fb"><span class="section-number-3">4.3</span> 入口の寸法</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-4-3">
<p>
入口は３箇所。各入口の寸法は表<a href="#org1ee8b04">3</a>。
</p>
<table id="org1ee8b04" border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides">
